verses.roman:
jaya jaya mahāprabhu śrī-kṛṣṇa-caitanya
jaya jaya nityānanda jayādvaita dhanya

synonyms: jaya jaya—all glories; mahāprabhu—Mahāprabhu; śrī-kṛṣṇa-caitanya—of the name Śrī Kṛṣṇa Caitanya; jaya jaya—all glories; nityānanda—to Lord Nityānanda Prabhu; jaya advaita—all glories to Advaita Prabhu; dhanya—who are all very glorious.
translation: All glories to Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu! All glories to Lord Nityānanda! All glories to Śrī Advaita Prabhu! All of Them are glorious.
